daily_fact: The 'Gold Standard' Open Street is on track to transform into a true 'Paseo Park,' offering two innovative paths forward that will enhance community space and connectivity in New York City.
topline_md: New York City is bracing for chilly Thanksgiving weather with wind gusts up to 35 mph, while Mayor-elect Zohran Mamdani has requested the resignation of 179 staffers from the previous administration, amidst ongoing discussions about civil lawsuits for sex abuse claims and new regulations on AI and rent-setting algorithms.
